{"tid":2133203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派Plan B Plan C今報名","createTime":"2020-07-31T02:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T04:16:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c70c837f1c81f8f10e6bbea71b8357fae659af4f","tid":2133203,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/KY5RLW44ABLVRW6RDQ2J5BF2XA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FKY5RLW44ABLVRW6RDQ2J5BF2XA%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1xzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=65aeaa52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FKY5RLW44ABLVRW6RDQ2J5BF2XA%2F&h=7d00bd9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/KY5RLW44ABLVRW6RDQ2J5BF2XA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民主派Plan B Plan C今報名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f4UATLJUQgMujbcVTvcZQuw7xNU=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSROLBPQ5KQHENJP662R5D66PY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff4UATLJUQgMujbcVTvcZQuw7xNU%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSROLBPQ5KQHENJP662R5D66PY.jpg&h=1f0226c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許智峯<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政權昨日大舉DQ民主派立法會參選人，涉及激進與溫和光譜，程度之廣被視為超出預期，但其實早在民主派在協調初選時，因當局明確表態針對35+，故此均有作出最壞打算，更已擬定後備名單。據知若提名期結束前，民主派參選人仍未獲確認提名，他們的Plan B甚至Plan C將會把握今日最後一天提名期報名。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：恐全軍覆沒 公民黨誓與港人並肩<br />\n<br />\n民主黨或派非黨員出戰<br />\n<br />\n公民黨昨在記者會上被多番追問Plan B安排時，黨主席梁家傑稱，以選舉主任DQ裁決理據可見，DQ公民黨純屬政治操作，相信該黨即使派出Plan B人選亦只會是「凍過水」，故暫未打算派Plan B參選；黨魁楊岳橋則笑稱：「就算有都唔話畀你知啦！」<br />\n<br />\n一直未有接獲選舉主任來函查詢的民主黨，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據知，不同政黨及組織早已商討過Plan B甚至Plan C的問題，有知情者私下透露，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有民主陣營中人分析，終極最壞結果是不同後備名單最終被全數DQ無法參選，不排除當局為阻止35+發生而無所不用其極，如果真的發生，已等同宣告整場選舉被全面操控，參選也失去意義，政權此舉肯定會激怒港人，屆時大可推動投白票，「如果最後白票數目係多過建制派得票，已經一定係國際笑話，已經唔需要香港人出聲，國際都一定會做嘢」。"},{"pid":"c8b2f0389e3b2ebf2092f291bafe6d3852cc33b1","tid":2133203,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"許智峯99.9% dq"},{"pid":"5372d2d1eff4272a3050399a993f51c654ee826a","tid":2133203,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8b2f0389e3b2ebf2092f291bafe6d3852cc33b1","tid":2133203,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"許智峯99.9% dq"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"只怕佢唔dq民主黨"},{"pid":"71f58da22732bcfd8df8935738b793c1d5e59482","tid":2133203,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"政府要分化民主派"},{"pid":"efe314c4487c1dcf935c042c17bb4a7a3d6b22c4","tid":2133203,"uid":212681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"不斷DQ,最後黃碧雲上場？"},{"pid":"8c5134c58fd69c0b52a371b825e465828689c6fe","tid":2133203,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2390a998e32ea353320b2583869550e65ef89c7c","tid":2133203,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:17:40.000Z","msg":"港共政府逼人投建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbfd58a95848546d488f87f637773e2e0bb3945","tid":2133203,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港共政府逼人投建制即係叫人投白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e14b10c83c19828f95263b2105992c0d5470ca40","tid":2133203,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"政府専登搵批爛頭卒黎做dq主任，總之無政黨或背後係泛民嘅都唔俾你選立會。不如除消立法會，拆埋座大樓啦"},{"pid":"72d73f387fb00988af3b145593edffb9977e74ad","tid":2133203,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike"